  14,45,And you dwelt in the dwellings of those who had wronged their own souls; and it was made plain to you how We dealt with them; and We struck out many parables for you
  14,46,"But they plotted mighty stratagems, but their stratagem were within AllahÂ´s sight, although their stratagem were mountain-shaking"
  14,47,"So think not that Allah fails in his promise to His Messengers. Verily, Allah is Mighty, the Lord of Retribution"
  14,48,"On the day when the earth shall be changed for another earth, and the heavens too; and all shall come forth unto Allah, the One, the Almighty"
  14,49,You shall see the guilty on that day bound together in chains
  14,50,"With garments of pitch, and fire covering their faces"
  14,51,"That Allah may reward each soul according to what it has earned. Verily, Allah is swift at reckoning"
  14,52,"This is a clear message to be delivered to mankind that they may be warned thereby, and that they may know that only He is Allah, the One, and that men of understanding may take heed"